### 28 Shaka Gutungana
  **1**   
 Shaka gutungana, Jy'uhor'usenga;
Bana n'Uwiteka, Ujy'umwumvira;
Jy'ukund'Abakristo, Fash'abarembye;
Ntuhuge na hato, Gushak'ihirwe.

  **2**   
Shaka gutungana, Hagomye benshi;
Horana na Yesu, Mu rwiherero. N'umwitegereza, Uzaba nka we;
Bose bazamenya, K'umeze nka we. 

  **3**   
Shaka gutungana, Akuyobore.
 Ty'itond'imbere ye, N'ugir'ibyago,
 Uk'umera kose, Jy'umwiyambaza.
 Jy'uyoboka Yesu, Mwumvire rwose. 

  **4**   
Shaka gutungana, Tuz'umutima.
 Tekerez'ibyiza, Wihutiraho.
 Jya wumvir'Umwuka, Gwiz'urukundo;
Uzatunganira, Kuba mw'ijuru.

### 40 Tubane N'Uwami   

  **1**   
 Tubane n'Umwami, Twumvir'ijambo rye;
Atujyana mu nzira nziza, Tumwumviye rwose. Akabana natwe, N'abamwizer'uko bangana.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
Jy'umwumvira, Nta kandi gakiza, Keretse Yesu gusa;
Mwizigire rwose.

  **2**   
Ntihakingirizwa, Nta gicu gikuba, Byeyurwa no kumwenyura kwe. Nta shiti n'ubwoba, Bona n'igishyika, Bimarwa n'uko tumwizeye. 

  **3**   
Nta kitubabaza, Nta shavu tugira;
Niw'uduhembur'imbu zose;
Nta bworo n'isari, Nta n'umubabaro;
Tuzahirwa ni tumwizera. 

  **4**   
Ntabwo twiyungura, Kugir'ibyishimo, Kugeza ko tureka byose, Kubw'imbabazi ze;
Impan'ajy'atanga, N'ingororano z'abizeye. 

  **5**   
Tuzajya twishima, Turi kumwe nawe. Tuzagendana naw'iteka, Tumwumvira rwose;
Azajy'adutuma, Ntacyo tuzaba tugitinya.

### 77 Nkunda Kwogez'Amagambo   

  **1**   
 Nkunda kwogez'amagambo, Y'ubwami bwo mw'ijuru;
Ya Yesu n'ishimwe rye, Ya Yesu n'urukundo rwe. Niyo nkunda kwogeza, Kuko nzi kw'ar'ukuri;
Niy'amp'ibyo nifuza, Nta handi mbibona.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
Niyo nkunda kwogeza;
Nkize nzaba nkivuga, Ukw'ab'isi bahoranye, Impuhwe za Yesu.

  **2**   
Nkunda kwogez'amagambo, Arut'ibintu byose;
Ahebuz'umurimbo;
N'ibyo turigira byose, Niyo nkunda kwogeza. Yangiriy'umumaro;
Simpwema kuyarata, Ngw abakize namwe. 

  **3**   
Nkunda kwogez'amagambo, Nkomeze njye nyavuga;
Aranogera cyane, Kukw'ambwiriz'iby'ijuru;
Niyo nkunda kwogeza, Nyabwir'abatayazi, Bameny'ako gakiza, Kava mu nzandiko. 

  **4**   
Nkunda kwogez'amagambo, Nyabwira n'abayazi, N'abayakennye nabo, Bose bashaka kuyumva. Ubwo nzaba mw'ijuru, Ndirimb'indirimbo nshya, Nay'izab'impimbaye, Nk'amagambo nkunda.

### 85 Nsingiz'Imana Rurema   

  **1**   
 Nsingiz'Imana Rurema, Yaremy'imisozi;
Yadendej'inyanja zose, Yahanits'ijuru;
Nsingiz'iyahay'izuba, Kumurika mu munsi. Ih'ukwezi kubonesha, N'inyenyer'umucyo.

  **2**   
Nsingiz'ibambe ry'Umwami, Wujuj'is'imyaka;
Yaremeshej'ijambo rye, Ibizima byose. Mwami mbon'ibitangaza, Byaw'aho ndeba hose, Hano hasi no hejuru, Ntabwo bihinyuka. 

  **3**   
Nta kiriho na gitoya, Kitakwerekana. Imvura n'izuba biba, Kw'itegeko ryawe. Uh'ibizima kubaho, Kand'ubitunga byose. Ntaho twahungir'Imana, Kuko ntahw'itaba.

### 101 Yesu Araguhamagara None   

  **1**   
 Yes'araguhamagara none, Arakwifuz'uyu munsi;
N'iki gituma wanga kwitaba, Ukayobagurika?

  **Gusubiramo:**   
   S. na A.: Uyu munsi, uyu munsi ;
Yes'araguhamagaran'imbabazi ze.
    T. na B.: Uyu munsi, none, none;
Uyu munsi, none, none;
Yesu Yes'Umwami ni w'Uguhamagaran'imbabazi ze.

  **2**   
Yes'arahamagar'abarushye, Ngw'abaruhur'uyu munsi;
Umwikorez'umutwaro wawe;
Ntazagushor'inshucu. 

  **3**   
Yes'aragutegereje none, Musange non'uyu munsi;
Zan'ibyaha byaw'ubyicujije, Ngwino witindiganya. 

  **4**   
Yes'arakwinginga, wumv'ijwi rye;
Mwumvire non'uyu munsi. Abamwiringira bazishima;
Haguruk'umusange!

### 104 Mucunguzi Wanjye   

  **1**   
 Mucunguzi wanjye, wumv'uko ntaka;
Ngwin'unyirokorere. Umutima wanjy'ugoswe n'ibyago;
Ngwin'unyirokorere.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
Nahabiye kure, nd'akahebwe;
Nahabiye kure y'iwacu. Nyakira none, maz'ungez'iwacu;
Ngwin'unyirokorere.

  **2**   
Mwami, singira shinge na rugero;
Ngwin'unyirokorere. Kwitabwaho nawe nibyo byanyura;
Ngwin'unyirokorere. 

  **3**   
Dore ndi jyenyine, nabay'impabe;
Ngwin'unyirokorere. Nubuy'amaso ngo mbeshweho nawe;
Ngwin'unyirokorere. 

  **4**   
Ntuhinyur'umutim'ushenjaguwe;
Ngwin'unyirokorere, Nyamunek'ita ku gusenga kwanjye, Ngwin'unyirokorere.

### 106 Twubake Ku Rutare Rw'Iteka   

  **1**   
 Twubake ku Rutare rw'iteka, Nirwo Yes'umucunguzi;
Nibwo tuzabasha gushikama, Umugaru n'utera.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
   Sop : Twubake kuri we, Twubake kuri we;
Twubake ku Rutare rw'iteka, Nirwo Yes'Umwami.
    A.T.B : Twubake kuri we, Niwe Rutare;
Twubake kuri we, Niwe Rutare;
Twubake ku Rutare rw'iteka, Nirwo Yes'Umwami.

  **2**   
Harihw'abubaka ku musenyi, Barangamiy'iby'iyi si;
Abandi bubaka ku muraba w'ibyaha no kwikuza. 

  **3**   
Twubake ku Rutare rw'ukuri, Nirwo rushikam'iteka. Kurwiringira kuzahoraho, Nirwo gakiza kacu.

### 107 Menyesh'Ibya Yesu Byose   

  **1**   
 Menyesh'ibya Yesu byose, Maz'ubinyandikemo;
Mbwir'ibye by'ingenzi byose, Nezezwa no kubyumva. Mbwir'ukw'abamarayika baririmbye yavutse, Ngw'Icyubahiro ku Mana, Amahoro abe mu b'isi.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
Menyesh'ibya Yesu byose, Maz'ubinyandikemo. Mbwir'ibye by'ingenzi byose, Nezezwa no kubyumva.

  **2**   
Mbwira n'ibyo mu butayu, N'iminsi yahamaze;
N'uburyo yageragejwe, Agatsind'ibishuko;
Mbwira n'iby'imirimo ye, Vug'uko yababajwe;
Agahemurwa bamwanze, Agahinyurwa nk'impabe. 

  **3**   
Mbwir'iby'umusaraba we, Uwo bamubambyeho, Mbwira n'aho bamuhambye, Mbwira n'uko yazutse, N'urukundo ruhebuje, Ntacyo narugeraho. Dore, ndababaye, mbwira iby'urukundo rwancunguye.

### 108 Yes'Umwungeri Mwiza   

  **1**   
 Yes'Umwungeri mwiza, Aragutarura, Ngo winjire mw'ishyo rye;
Nih'uzaruhukira. Ngwin'ugif'ubusore, Ngwin'ukiri muto;
Injir'uzarindwa rwose, Ntuzagir'icy'uganya.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
Aragutaruran'urukundo, ati: Wa mpabe we, ngwino nsanga. Dor'Umukiz'arategereje, Yes'Umwungeri wanjye

  **2**   
Yes'Umwungeri mwiza, Yarakwitangiye;
Araguhamagara ati: Nyabuna ngwino, Gira bwang'uve mu kaga, Ntugumye, kwijyana. Injir'uzarindwa rwose, Wibere mu mahoro. 

  **3**   
Reka kuragiriza, Isega yateye, Ishak'intama zose, Zazimiriye kure. Arik'Umwungeri mwiza, Arakuburira;
Injir'uzarindwa rwose, Muban'akaramata.

### 113 Yesu Araguhamagaran'Ituza   

  **1**   
 Yes'araguhamagaran'ituza, Ub'arahamagara;
Ategereje k'umwiyegurira, We kuzuyaza;
ngwino.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
Ngwino ( ngwino);
Ngwino (ngwino);
Abarushye mwese nimuze. Yes'araguhamagaran'ituza, ati: Mukundwa, ngwino.

  **2**   
Twatinzwa n'iki, kand'ategereje kuturokora twese?
Twahinyuzwa n'ik'imbabazi zose adufitiye twese? 

  **3**   
Twakererew'ibihe birahita, Aradutegereje;
Turarindagirira mu mwijima;
Nimutyo tumusange. 

  **4**   
Zirikan'urukundo ruhebuje, Yadusezeranije;
N'ubwo twagomye, Tuzababarirwa;
Aradutegereje.

### 118 Ndumv'Umukiz'Ambwira   

  **1**   
 Ndumv'Umukiz'ambwira, Ko mbuz'imbaraga;
Ngo: Njye museng'iteka, Ntacyo nzamuburana.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
Yanndihiriye imyenda yose;
Yambabariy'ibyaha, Bihinduk'umweru.

  **2**   
Niw'ufit'imbaraga, Zihagije rwose;
Zo gukiz'ababembe, Zikoroshy'umutima. 

  **3**   
Ubwo nta cyiza nkora, Nibesherejweho;
N'ubuntu bwawe gusa, Ni wowe nkesha byose. 

  **4**   
Imbere ya ya ntebe, Nzahahagarara;
Nzaba njyany'iminyago, Nyishyikirize Yesu.

### 120 Data Ndambuy'Amaboko   

  **1**   
 Data, ndambuy'amaboko;
Nta wundi wamfasha;
Iy'unyivumburiy'ukamvaho, Mbes'ahandi najya ni he?

  **2**   
Nizey'Umwana waw'ubu, Undem'umutima;
Ujy'unkenur'umar'ubukene, Nkomeze nemerwe nawe. 

  **3**   
Nyir'ukwizera ni wowe, Nuburiy'amaso;
Icyamp'ukangwiriza kwizera, Kuko ntagufite napfa. 

  **4**   
Ntuzantererane ngo mpfe, Ahubw'umbesheho;
Nibwo nzacika ku kinyoma, Mbishobojwe n'Umwuka wawe. 

  **5**   
Nakwishima cyane rwose, Nibaniye nawe;
Maze nkakumv'umpumuriz'umbwira ko nagiriw'ubuntu. 

  **6**   
Nizeye rwos'ubu yuko, Yesu yampfiriye;
Kandi kubw'amaraso ye yeza, Nzabaturwa mve mu byaha.

### 122 Nyigiza Hafi   

  **1**   
 Nyigiza hafi, mbane nawe;
Nta cyandutira kubana nawe. Ngumisha mu gituza cyawe;
Mpisha nibere mu buhungiro;
Mpisha nibere mu buhungiro.

  **2**   
Nyigiza hafi, ntacyo mfite;
Ntacyo nzanyehw'ituro ry'Umwami, Kerets'umutim'ushavuye;
Mpa kuhagizw'amaraso yawe;
Mpa kuhagizw'amaraso yawe. 

  **3**   
Nyigiza hafi, Mwami wanjye;
Nishimiye gucika ku byaha. Ndeke kwikuza n'ubwibone;
Umpe Yes'Umwami wambambiwe;
Umpe Yes'Umwami wambambiwe. 

  **4**   
Nyigiza hafi, ngihumeka;
Kugez'ubwo nzager'i Budapfa;
Maze mu bihe bidashira, Nzibere hafi y'Umwami wanjye;
Nzibere hafi y'Umwami wanjye.

### 124 Yesu Gusa   

  **1**   
 Yesu gusa, niw'ukwiriy'ikuzo;
Naho jyewe, ntacyo ndi cyo rwose;
Sinkwiriye kub'ari jyew'uratwa;
Yesu gusa, niw'uzajy'uvugwa.

  **2**   
Yesu gusa, niw'umar'agahinda;
Naho jyewe nd'uwo gushavura. Sinshobora kwikorer'ibindushya;
Naho Yesu nta kimushengura. 

  **3**   
Yesu gusa, ab'ari we wogezwa;
Sinkwiriye kwiratan'ibyanjye. Yesu gusa, niw'uzambonekamo;
Kugez'ubwo nzahinduka nka we. 

  **4**   
Yesu gusa niw'umar'ubukene;
Niwe gusa nkesh'ibyanjye byose. Yesu gusa, niw'undutira byose;
Yesu Mwami twibanir'iteka.

 ### 127 Iman'Ikund'Utunyoni   

  **1**   
 Iman'ikund'utunyoni, Tuba mur'iyi si;
Ubwo yita ku tunyoni, Nzi ko nanjy'inkunda.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
Irankunda, irankunda;
Nzi ko nanjy'inkunda;
Kukw'ikund'utuntu duto, Nzi ko nanjy'inkunda.

  **2**   
Niy'irimbish'uburabyo, Buhumura neza;
Ubw'ikund'uburaby'ityo, Nzi ko nanjy'inkunda. 

  **3**   
Imana yaremye byose, Ntigir'icy'isobwa. Nzi kw'ikund'abana bose, Nzi ko nanjy'inkunda.

### 131 Ndusheho Gusa Nawe   

  **1**   
 Ndusheho gusa nawe, Yesu Mukiza wanjye;
Nyuzuz'ubugwaneza, Mp'urukundo ruhebuje. Ndusheho kumera nkawe, Aho ngenda hose, Mwami;
Ndiyoroheje rwose, Mwami njye ngukurikiza.

  **2**   
Nib'irind'icyanira, Ikamenya n'igishwi;
Sinshidikanya rwose, Nanjy'ihor'inyitayeho. Izanyigisha kwitonda, Imbabarir'amafuti;
Ndiyoroheje rwose, Mwami njye ngukurikiza. 

  **3**   
Ndusheho gusa nawe, Ndusheh'uko bukeye;
Nyigiza hafi yawe, Ahw'amahor'adashira. Uhor'umpindura mushya, Kubw'urukund'ungirira;
Ndiyoroheje rwose, Mwami njye ngukurikiza.

### 133 Nyemerera Ngendane Nawe   

  **1**   
 Nyemerera ngendane nawe, Mana, Nk'ukw'Enoki yagenje. Nyoboresh'ukuboko kwawe, Unyerekez'ah'ushaka hose. Nubw'inzir'itagaragara, Nkomeze njyane nawe, Mwami.

  **2**   
Ntabwo nahangara kugenda, Ntari kumwe nawe, Mukiza;
Nagoswe n'abanz'igihumbi;
Dor'imitegw'intaye hagati. Burije rwose, ntihabona, Nkomeze njyane nawe, Mwami. 

  **3**   
Ninguma mu maboko yawe, Sinzaba ncyitaye ku by'isi;
Nta kindi nziratana rwose, Keretse wa musaraba wawe, Ngez'ubwo nzager'i Siyoni, Nkomeze njyane nawe, Mwami.

### 138 Mwami Wanjye, Nyakira   

  **1**   
 Mwami wanjye nyakira, Ndakwiyeguriy'ubu;
Ngay'amaboko yanjye, Yakoresh'uk'ushaka.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
Nyuhagiz'amaraso yawe ( nere rwose );
Maz'anyezehw'inenge yose ( nere rwose );
Ibyanjye byose ndabikweguriye, None n'iteka ryose.

  **2**   
Ngib'ibirenge byanjye, Byerekez'ah'ushaka. Ngir'ijwi ryanjye na ryo, Rijye riguhimbaza. 

  **3**   
Nguhay'akanwa kanjye;
Mwami, kakuvugire. Ngub'ubutunzi bwanjye, Sinzagir'icyo nkwima. 

  **4**   
Nguhay'igihe cyanjye, Sinzakiguteraho;
Nguhay'ubwenge bwanjye, Bukoresh'uk'ushaka. 

  **5**   
Ngiy'imigambi yanjye;
Igengwe nawe, Mwami. Nguy'umutima wanjye, Ube uwawe rwose. 

  **6**   
Mwam'urukundo rwanjye, Ni wowe nzarukunda;
Nkwihaye nimazeyo, None n'iteka ryose.

### 140 Numvise Yesu Ambwira Ati   

  **1**   
 Numvise Yes'ambwir'ati: Ngwino nkuruhure. Zan'ibikurushya byose, Mbikwikorerere. Musanga, mez'uko nari ndi, ndushye, mfite n'ishavu;
Amber'uburuhukiro, Maz'aranezeza.

  **2**   
Numvise Yes'ambwir'ati: Ndaguher'ubuntu, Amaz'azakubeshaho, Unyw'uram'iteka. Nuko nsanga Yesu maz'ampa ya mazi y'ubugingo, Nshir'inyota, Ndahembuka;
Nzahorana nawe. 

  **3**   
Numvise Yes'ambwir'ati: Ni jye Mucyo w'isi. N'undeb'uramurikirwa, Ntuzarindagira. Maze muhanz'amaso koko, Mbon'ar'izuba ryanjye;
Rizamvir'iminsi yose y'ubugingo bwanjye.

### 141 Mwami Mb'Uwawe Maramaje   

  **1**   
 Mwami, mb'uwawe maramaje, Nyigisha, nyigisha. Nkor'iby'ukunda, Mwami wanjye;
Komez'umfashe.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
Mb'uwawe ( Mwami ) ;
Mb'uwawe ( Mwami ) ;
Niyo migambi yanjye ;
Mb'uwawe ( Mwami ) ;
Mb'uwawe ( Mwami ) ;
Mb'uwawe Mwami, None.

  **2**   
Iby'iyi si byamarir'iki, Ntari kumwe nawe?
Byose nzabihara kubwawe, Ntungishwe nawe. 

  **3**   
Ndets'umunezero w'iyi si, Ngwino twibanire;
Nibyo bizajya binogera, Bimpumurize.

### 143 Udusezeresh'Umugisha Wawe   

  **1**   
 Udusezeresh'umugisha wawe;
Mwam'utwuzuz'amahoro;
Urukundo rwawe rudusabemo, Tubone kunesha rwose. Ngwin'uduhembure, Ngwin'uduhembure;
Tukiri mur'iyi si y'igomero.

  **2**   
Tuguhay'ishimwe no kukuramya, Kubw'ubutumwa bw'imvaho, Bwagukomotseho bukadukiza, Bunyur'imitima yacu;
Tubushikamemo, Tubushikamemo;
Tugundir'ukuri, Tudacogora. 

  **3**   
Mbeshwaho n'imbabazi zawe nyinshi, None ndakwiyeguriye. Ngwin'uduhumurish'impuhwe zawe, Duhore turwan'ishyaka;
Tuzager'i wawe, Tuzager'iwawe;
Tukubone nta kidukingirije.

### 144 Mukiza, Ndamaramaje   

  **1**   
 Mukiza, ndamaramaje, Ndatwaranira kugera, Ku rugero runkwiriye;
Mwami mfasha ngo ndusheho.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
Nzamura maze nger'aho wangeneye, Mwami wanjye;
Ku rugero rusumbyeho;
Mwami mfasha ngo ndusheho.

  **2**   
Ntabwo ngifit'umutima, Wo kuguma mu by'iyi si;
N'ubwo bamwe babikunda, Ngambiriye kujya mbere. 

  **3**   
Ndashaka gusumb'iby'isi, Nubw'umwanz'anyibasiye;
Kuko namaze kwizera, Yukw'Iman'izandengera. 

  **4**   
Ndashaka kumaranira, Kurabukw'ubwiza bwawe;
Ariko nkomeze nsenge, Ngez'ubwo nzager'i wawe.

### 145 Ntushak'Urwitwazo   

  **1**   
 Ntushak'urwitwazo, Harihw'imirimo, Ahubw'itegure gukorer'Imana. Yakwinginze kenshi, Kand'ikurarika;
Witinda kwemera, Bizakunezeza.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
Itaba! ( none );
Ntushak'urwitwazo;
Itaba! ( none );
Wigingimiranya. Ntushak'urwitwazo, Udasubizwa ngo: Hoshi wampinyuye;
Nkuvukij'ubwami.

  **2**   
Ntushak'urwitwazo urahamagawe;
Dor'aho wangiye, Noneho witabe. Imirim'ireze, Hagumy'abakozi;
Ngwin'umukorere;
Uzagororerwa. 

  **3**   
Ntushak'urwitwazo, Kuko nib'utinze, Bizagukoraho, Izakwivumbura. Imbabazi zayo, Ntabwo zirashira;
Haguruka bwangu, Ubibabarirwe.

### 147 Data Mwiza, Nyigiza Hafi   

  **1**   
 Data mwiza, nyigiza hafi;
Nkube mu gituza;Ni wowe buhungiro bwanjye, N'uburuhukiro.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
   S. na A : Data, nyigiza hafi, Ndifuza ko tubana;
Data, ndifuza ko tubana.
    T. na B : Data, data, nyigiza hafi, Ndifuza cyane ko tubana;
Data, nyigiza hafi;
ndifuza ko tubana, Ndifuza ko tubana.

  **2**   
Data mwiza, nyigiza hafi;
Nkomeza ntundeke;
Nakwishimira ko tubana, Ne kuraragira. 

  **3**   
Data mwiza, nyigiza hafi;
Ngez'ubwo nsa nawe;
Mpembur'unyuhagir'unyeze, Mb'umuziranenge.

### 149 Nshuti Jy'ugendera Mu Mucyo   

  **1**   
 Nshuti jy'ugendera mu mucyo, Woye kurindagira;
Umwuka Wera wo mw'ijuru, Ajy'akuyobora.

  **Gusubiramo:**   
   S. na A :Gendera mu mucyo, Gendera mu mucyo;
Gendera mu mucyo, Mu mucyo waka w'Imana.
    T. na B. :Gendera mu mucy'utangaje w'Imana;
Gendera mu mucy'utangaje w'Imana;
Gendera mu mucy'utangaje w'Imana;
Mu mucyo waka w'Imana;

  **2**   
Gendera mu mucyo w'ukuri, Ko mw'Ijambo ry'Imana;
Uzajy'ukuyobor'iteka, Ukwizez'Imana. 

  **3**   
Jy'ugendera mu mucy'iteka, Ujy'ukumurikira;
Maz'utamurur'umwijima, Hose hatangaze. 

  **4**   
Gendera mu mucyo ng'umenye, Urukundo rw'Imana, N'uburyo yakunze ab'isi, Ikabarokora.

### 153 Mwami, Sinsabir'Iby'Ejo   

  **1**   
 Mwami, sinsabir'iby'ejo, Mfasha none, Ndind'urukongi rw'ibyaha, Uyu munsi. Ne gucumuz'ururimi, Mputiyeho;
Mwami, rind'iminwa yanjye, Uyu munsi.

  **2**   
Njye nshunguz'ubury'umwete, No gusenga;
Ngwe neza mu buryo bwose, Uyu munsi. Nkomeze nkor'iby'ushaka, Ngire bwangu;
Mwami, nemere kwitanga, Uyu munsi. 

  **3**   
Urupfu niruntungura, Mbe ntunganye;
